{
  "stem": "25639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His brothers and his sister were all gassed in Auschwitz upon arrival, and most of their children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So here, in one war, they were the heroes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In another war, they were subhumans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I, I know that it started much before, or long before I became aware of it because Jewish men started disappearing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- eventually, their wives would receive a letter that they died on the-- on the Russian front, all of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But word tickled down-- trickled down that they were murdered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people didn't know how this happened, and we could sometimes imagine that somebody just took a gun and, and shot them-- shot them at random.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how it worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is not-- I am not an eyewitness to that, but, but I know my uncle disappeared that way, leaving behind six children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were many in our town who disappeared that way, including our shohet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So today, even to date, we, we can only conjecture how they died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later, much later, the men talked about-- after the Holocaust-- a few men, that is, who returned, talked about how these people were taken out, and they were-- they were shot into the river.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I never heard that when I was home, so I hesitate talking about something that I did not witness because I do have a lot of eyewitness accounts to tell at this filming.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were-- it began in '38.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we kept our cattle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We kept our house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we lived as we normally did, except that it became abnormal because the income from the store wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The, the-- our entire lives totally shifted to the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That became a godsend to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
